liating them and \"putting them in their place\". I hated the climactic interaction with kids at school. I thought the tacked-on Penny ending was completely unnecessary. The book had really great potential, and I still think that the perspective is important to tell, but I haven't disliked a character so much since I had to suffer through \u003ca href=\"https://goodreads.com/book/show/6098148.The_Girls_from_Ames_A_Story_of_Women_and_a_Forty_Year_Friendship\" title=\"The Girls from Ames A Story of Women and a Forty-Year Friendship by Jeffrey Zaslow\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eThe Girls from Ames\u003c/a\u003e. ","rating":2,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/985163?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"elementary-school","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/985163?shelf=elementary-school"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"k-6","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/985163?shelf=k-6"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"realistic","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/985163?shelf=realistic"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"prejudice","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/985163?shelf=prejudice"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"disabilities-disorders","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/985163?shelf=disabilities-disorders"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/174260047"},"likeCount":57,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":39,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:14514998":{"id":14514998,"__typename":"User","legacyId":14514998,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1632159916i/14514998._UY200_CR33,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":1637,"viewableName":"Rachel Reads Ravenously","isBloc