 machine gives her the ability to speak, not everyone is ready to accept her as \"normal\".\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eSharon Draper is a brilliant writer. Words flow across the page effortlessly and I am wowed at how she captured and portrayed Melody. I want everyone to read this book. It's so special and it shows us how our perceptions are not always accurate,\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1494101706i/22685352._SX540_.png\" class=\"gr-hostedUserImg\" loading=\"lazy\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003eFollow me on ♥ \u003ca href=\"http://www.facebook.com/rachelreadsravenously\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eFacebook\u003c/a\u003e ♥ \u003ca href=\"http://rachelsreadsravenously.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eBlog\u003c/a\u003e ♥ \u003ca href=\"http://instagram.com/rachelreadsravenously\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eInstagram\u003c/a\u003e ♥ \u003ca href=\"https://twitter.com/rayliz89\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eTwitter\u003c/a\u003e ♥","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/14514998?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"paperback","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/14514998?shelf=paperback"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"middle-grade-or-childrens","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/14514998?shelf=middle-grade-or-childrens"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2612499318"},"likeCount":52,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":5,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:5211606":{"id":5211606,"__typename":"User","legacyId":5211606,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1505571524i/5211606._UX200_CR0,11,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":788,"viewableName":"Julie","isBlockedByViewer":false,"